snippet: Derrick Favors scored a career-high 32 points and added nine rebounds, Gordon Hayward had 24 points and 10 boards, and the Utah Jazz beat the Phoenix Suns 118-91 on Saturday night....

headline.print_headline: Favors Powers Jazz to First Win, 118-91 Over Suns
headline.main: Favors Powers Jazz to First Win, 118-91 Over Suns

lead_paragraph: Derrick Favors scored a career-high 32 points and added nine rebounds, Gordon Hayward had 24 points and 10 boards, and the Utah Jazz beat the Phoenix Suns 118-91 on Saturday night.
